# Cart Management Module

This module enables customers to add, update, and remove products from their shopping cart, providing a seamless shopping experience before checkout. It keeps prices and quantities updated in real time and includes dashboards for customer and admin review.

---

## üìã Features

### 1. Add to Cart
- Customers can add products directly from product pages.
- The system checks inventory before allowing an item to be added.

### 2. Update Cart
- Customers can change item quantities.
- Price updates automatically; stock is revalidated.

### 3. Remove from Cart
- Items can be removed instantly.
- Total price recalculates.

### 4. Cart Dashboard
- Customers see cart items, price, quantity, total.
- Admins analyze all carts and review abandonment rates.

---

## üóÑÔ∏è Database Design

**Database Name:** `VIBGYOR`  
**Table Name:** `carts`

| Column Name   | Data Type                | Description                               |
|---------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| cart_id       | INT, PK, AUTO_INCREMENT | Unique ID for each cart                   |
| customer_id   | INT, FK                 | References users(user_id)                 |
| product_id    | INT, FK                 | References products(product_id)           |
| quantity      | INT                     | Item count in cart                        |
| total_price   | DECIMAL(10,2)           | Total price of cart items                 |
| created_at    | DATETIME                | Cart creation timestamp                   |
| updated_at    | DATETIME                | Last updated timestamp                    |

